name: VikingRaid
0:
”Alexa, launch Viking Raid”
”Alexa, ask Viking Raid to attack”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: viking raid
des:
Do the neighbors have too much gold? Feel like expanding the amount of land under your control? Itching to send your family members in a small boat across a vast ocean to plunder the docile masses? 

Then you've come to the right place! 
Send in the Vikings!

Viking Raid allows your to launch an imaginary attack on your target of choice! Have fun and may Odin guide your way!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
